<![CDATA[<font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;">Hello&nbsp;<b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!Bug_Log__c.Owner__c}</b><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;!&nbsp;</b></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">Please noticed that your<b>&nbsp;</b></font><font size="2"><b>{!Bug_Log__c.Name}</b>&nbsp;is in the status:&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><b>{!Bug_Log__c.Status__c}</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style=""><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">Follow the link :&nbsp;</font></font><font size="2"><font face="arial" style="font-family: arial;">&nbsp;</font></font><font face="arial" size="2" style="font-family: arial;">https://carmignac-crm.lightning.force.com/</font><font face="arial" size="2" style="font-family: arial;">lightning/r/Bug_Log__c/{!Bug_Log__c.Id}/view</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Don't forget to check your notifications or add any comments on your chatter log that can help&nbsp;</font><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">{!Bug_Log__c.AssignedTo__c} to resolve your case</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font size="2" style=""><font face="Arial, sans-serif" style="">Best regards !&nbsp;</font><font face="arial" style="">&nbsp;</font></font></div>]]></td>
